data.description: Great find in a lovely neighborhood with a 3-car garage! This 4 bed, 3 bath home boasts of all new kitchen appliances, all new flooring - wood, carpet, vinyl, and new plumbing fixtures!! The home backs up to a peaceful wooded area w all sorts of wildlife. The sunny eat-in kitchen w new wood floors has a large center island, and tons of counter space and cabinets. The formal dining room showcases the new wood floors and opens out onto private deck space. Laundry in main floor mudroom. Upper bedrooms & living room have view of the woods. Enjoy cozy nights in front of fireplace in the LL family room. LL bedroom has built-in shelving, perfect for a home office. New roof 2022. Great schools. Tons of storage. Bring your ideas for paint colors. Only minutes to the freeway. Schedule a private showing today!
